# basics.p0t — a minimal test-engine suite (gen345).
# Run by: make test  (which pipes every tests/p0t/*.p0t into one engine instance)
# Syntax: docs/plans/test-engine.md — `>` a turn, `<` the expected reply.

[test greeting]
> hello
< Hi there!

[test arithmetic]
> what is 12 * 12
< 144.

[test capital-known]
> what is the capital of france
< Paris.

[test taxonomy]
> is a tiger a mammal
< Yes.

[test antonym]
> what is the opposite of hot
< Cold.
